[New Wave Project Audition, Central Region Qualifying Round]

18
00:01:22,568 --> 00:01:23,276
Moo.

19
00:01:23,835 --> 00:01:24,791
Go get ‘em.

20
00:01:24,987 --> 00:01:25,840
I will.

21
00:01:28,187 --> 00:01:28,959
Can you take this?

22
