I have to go.

23
00:01:29,534 --> 00:01:30,034
Hurry.

24
00:01:32,968 --> 00:01:33,649
Kang.

25
00:01:34,459 --> 00:01:35,884
Give me a hug. I need some encouragement.

26
00:01:41,165 --> 00:01:42,000
I’m going now.

27
00:01:42,587 --> 00:01:43,406
Go kill it.

28
00:01:43,406 --> 00:01:44,536
I’m rooting for you.

29
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,251
You have 10 seconds.

30
00:01:49,983 --> 00:01:51,053
10.

